The Groupâ€™s entrepreneurial fortitude can be traced back to 1949 when the forefather, the late Mr. Kisanlal R. Kothari, sowed the seed with the inception of the Group. The same passion for delivering quality and thoughtfully expanding the business on the basis of worthwhile opportunities carries forward. And now Vinay and Vikas, while shouldering the responsibilities.
